Due to financial constraints, the club does not currently operate a reserve team, however it does field a youth team at Under-18 level<ref>{{Cite web
| url = http://www.gillinghamfootballclub.premiumtv.co.uk/page/YouthIndex/0,,10416,00.html
| title = Youth Fixtures
