| publisher = Gillingham F.C.
}}</ref> and operates a Centre of Excellence for boys in the Under-9 to Under-16 age groups.<ref>{{Cite web
| url = http://www.gillinghamfootballclub.premiumtv.co.uk/page/COEIndex/0,,10416,00.html
| title = Centre of Excellence
| accessdate = 2007-09-08
| publisher = Gillingham F.C.
}}</ref>

